  "name": "Fading Slide",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/open_hand.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you have martial focus, when a creature makes a melee attack or combat maneuver against you, you may spend an immediate action to make a touch attack against that creature, dealing damage equal to your practitioner modifier + your base attack bonus. Regardless of if your attack is successful or not, you then immediately fall prone (you may not use this talent if you are unable to become prone or already prone). At +10 base attack bonus, this talent instead deals damage equal to your unarmed strike.</p>\n",
